34
00:03:16.000 --> 00:03:21.000
And this retarget asset, I'll put into my temp folder,

35
00:03:21.000 --> 00:03:33.000
and it will create this auto-generated retargeting system that will try to match Manny's movements to Gaunt.

36
00:03:35.000 --> 00:03:41.000
And if I wanted to test this briefly, I could open up any of these animations

37
00:03:41.000 --> 00:03:47.000
and see how the two of them respond together to the same animations,

38
00:03:47.000 --> 00:03:53.000
even though they actually have different skeletons, and we can see it's working pretty well.

